content: Hello Jeyachandran J, welcome to the interview. I'm Master, your hiring officer. I'm excited to learn more about your technical skills and experience. Let's get started with the technical round. Can you walk me through your project, "Developed a web app for mock interviews utilizing AI to ask voice-based questions based on uploaded resumes, while students reply in text"? What was your role in this project, and what did you learn from it?
